queryResponse.sql:
-- raw sql results do not include filled-in values for 'shipments.dispatched_month'


SELECT
    (TO_CHAR(DATE_TRUNC('month', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(shipments.dispatched_at  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))), 'YYYY-MM')) AS "shipments.dispatched_month",
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (CASE WHEN shipments.is_tonu  THEN 1 ELSE 0 END
) = 0 THEN shipments.id  ELSE NULL END) AS "shipments.shipment_count"
FROM stark_prod.recreated_tables.shipments  AS shipments
WHERE ((( shipments.dispatched_at  ) >= ((CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(DATEADD('month', -12, DATE_TRUNC('month', DATE_TRUNC('day', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))))) AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))) AND ( shipments.dispatched_at  ) < ((CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(DATEADD('month', 13, DATEADD('month', -12, DATE_TRUNC('month', DATE_TRUNC('day', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))))) AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))))))
GROUP BY
    (DATE_TRUNC('month', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(shipments.dispatched_at  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))))
ORDER BY
    1 DESC
FETCH NEXT 500 ROWS ONLY
